reviewText: Interesting course but there is no certificate !

Hoped more from this course as from the description you would learn how to debug embedded systems and how is it done. The course is rated for "intermediate" but it is a total beginner course. The whole "course" should be 1 or 2 lectures on YouTube. No task, no assignments no interaction. Skimmed through the course in couple of days here and there were some interesting points, but that's it.
